product_name: Five Ten Chase Parkour and Freerunning Shoes - Women's - 2011 Closeout
long_description: Named after a famous freerunner/parkour athlete, the supportive Five Ten(R) women's Chase parkour and freerunning shoes help you balance on a rail and land a precision gap jump with ease. Synthetic nubuck and split-grain leather uppers are reinforced at key wear spots for rigorous use. Compression-molded EVA midsoles keep feet comfortable when the going gets rough. Stealth(R) S1(TM) high-friction rubber outsoles offer exceptional grip and durable wear. The Five Ten Chase parkour and freerunning shoes feature mesh linings to move moisture away from the feet for comfort. Closeout.
